    "This is a patient-administered questionnaire designed for follow-up assessments of different types of knee injuries.",
    "Its self-administered nature makes it convenient for patients to use, and its straightforward structure ensures ease of completion.",
    "Typically, it takes around 10 minutes for patients to complete the KOOS questionnaire.",
